data.description: Looking for a GARAGE with a house? Rare opportunity to own a 2-story outbuilding, featuring a 2-car wide overhead door, separate 1-car garage, workshop, with heated living/office space on the second floor. The building has its own central air unit, electric and gas meters, woodburning stove . . .great space for in-law living or a wood-worker's or mechanic's dream!! A 2-bedroom, 1-bath home comes with it! Updated with hardwood floors. Windows, roofs, water heater all replaced within the last ten years. Concrete block basement. Fenced yard. Radon mitigation system. A lot of potential here. Just needs some clean-up inside and out to be a gem. Great opportunity to build sweat equity!
